snippet.title: Super Scrap Sandbox  - Tutorial #1 How to build a simple vehicle
snippet.description:
Evertech Sandbox (Super Scrap Sandbox) is a game similar to Scrap Mechanic but for Android.
New link to download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.evertechsandbox
Old game removed: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.scrap.mechanic
